  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Overview",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Make your intents more discoverable to people by donating them to the"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "system. When someone performs an action in your app, donate an intent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "that corresponds to that action. The system uses the information you provide to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "predict actions someone might take in the future. For example, if someone",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "requests the weather from your app each morning, the system might proactively"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "offer the corresponding app intent at the same time each day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Donate intents only when someone uses your app’s interface directly. You",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "don’t need to donate intents associated with Siri or interactions with the"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Shortcuts app because the system donates them automatically. You can also"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "delete donations when someone cancels or reverses a previously executed action,"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "or when the action is no longer relevant.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
